Hey mane, this was actually a great upload. Probably one of the best I ever downloaded, truthfully. Audio/Video both a 9 outta 10. A very large viewing screen, and looks great in fullscreen. Thanks fer the upload!

I used VLC media player--very versatile. If you do not want the subtitles you can turn them off in VLC media player (Video>>Subtitles Track>>Disable). That easy. The media player you use also makes a huge difference. If yall aint never tried VLC i suggest you do. The vid plays awesome in VLC. VLC is free.
